<T>__{cut to:}
<B>__{underground tunnel}
<A>__{the group, carrying torches, moves along the dark tunnel. they pass a bubble window with shark faced eels swimming on the other side.}
<C>__{norl}
<P>__{(to den)}
<D>__{we're underneath the castle moat.}
<A>__{den nods. an ugly growl echoes through the tunnel up ahead. the warriors freeze and murmur to each other in their own languages.}
<C>__{den}
<P>__{(to norl)}
<D>__{what are they saying?}
<C>__{norl}
<D>__{they talk of the savage beast who prowls these catacombs with a fierce hunger and sharp teeth ...}
<P>__{(gestures)}
<D>__{six inches long.}
<A>__{a dog faced warrior shakes his head and says something to norl.}
<C>__{norl}
<D>__{sorry ...}
<P>__{(indicating)}
<D>__{...}
<A>__{sixteen inches long. suddenly, a savage beast appears and chomps his long, razor sharp teeth into one of the warriors at the end of the line. den, norl, and the remaining warriors run on through the tunnel as, behind them, the monster pulls his victim apart.}
